/>\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"e2b5396fed48d68fc1accfc3dc49c4b530ee75d4","tid":1662479,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:08:09.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有古怪喇"},{"pid":"82f5dcb202400eba66137ad76c4c51c7385bc616","tid":1662479,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:10:01.000Z","msg":"即係牧師逼佢自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481591a2a634b417bba500d0310a8a4bcbba895c","tid":1662479,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fc48e071e027f07e641353238996bddea637246","tid":1662479,"uid":333427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"當那日必有許多人對我說：『　主啊，　主啊，我們不是奉你的名說預言，奉你的名趕出鬼魔，奉你的名行過許多異能嗎？』<br />\n<br />\n我就明明的告訴他們說：『我從來不認識你們，你們這些作惡的人，離開我去吧！』<br />\n<br />\n（太7：22-23）<br />\n<br />\n我諗到末日之時，好多紅底牧師都會係咁講：咩我唔係傳福音咩？我間教會好多人黎架... 最後佢地都入唔到天國"},{"pid":"befaa07a28c8ebe4fd6630888c3bc4780aafb529","tid":1662479,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2667b8eaf86067819a773ab52469babfc06d7c8","tid":1662479,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"嘩，做咩咁有錢"},{"pid":"2a4769ff39afddc463a2bc684864277d81abb660","tid":1662479,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" 